############## Ansible Roles, Templates and Tags ###############

--> Roles are next level of ansible playbooks
--> we can re-use playbooks for different purposes, you can segregated server functionality, you can easy to maintain/trobleshooting playbooks.

handlers: event handlers (let's say you got one task once that task is finish succesfully it will call that handler or it will perform some actions).
depending upon your configuration).
meta: role dependencies
templates: similar to files, but it contains dynamic data.


